Asterisk puppet module
######################

Variants
########

Multiple variants exist:

  * include asterisk::voip-only
  
    VoIP only setup which does not require any specific hardware such as Zaptel card
  
  * include asterisk::with-zaptel

    Full setup including Zaptel kernel modules

Types
#####

  * asterisk::account::sip

    asterisk::account::sip {"1234":
      ensure  => present,
      secret  => "blah",
      context => "incoming"
    }

    asterisk::account::sip {"1234":
      ensure => absent
    }

  * asterisk::context

    asterisk::context {"incoming":
      ensure => present,
      source => ...
    }

    asterisk::context {"incoming":
      ensure  => present,
      content => template(...)
    }

    asterisk::context {"incoming":
      ensure => absent
    }

Still not implemented !
